_______________________________________________________________________________
"Brainwave"      
        This sends a mental wave through the room hitting everyone in
        its wake.  It has a low efficiency, costing more than a
        psionic blast but doing less damage to each individual target but
        it will hit every monster (and player, except the psionicist) in 
        the room.  It does less damage to players and pets.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  9		Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  bwave
